  <title>Table Components</title>
  
  <para><emphasis>Drag Cell</emphasis></para>
  <para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          This action drags the table cell you specify.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          The cell is specified by its row and column values.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          The cursor is moved over the cell.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          The mouse button you specify is held, and the cell is dragged.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          You must follow this action with a <emphasis>drop</emphasis> action.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Parameters:
          
          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="mouse_button"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="modifier_keys"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="row"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="row_operator"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="column"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="column_operator"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="x_position"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="x_units"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="y_position"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                <xref linkend="y_units"/>
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>
  
  <para>
    If you want to drag multiple items, use an action to select the items you want to drag before using the drag action.
  </para>
  
  <para role="tip">
    This action is unsupported for the HTML toolkit.
  </para>
  
