  <para><emphasis>Drop on Cell</emphasis></para>
  <para>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          This action drops a dragged item onto a cell you specify.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          The cell where the drop should occur is specified by its row and column values.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          The cursor is moved over the cell.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          The mouse button you specify is let loose, and the cell is dropped.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Precede this action with a <emphasis>drag</emphasis> action.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
